festival.introText: Taking place at The OVO Hydro in Glasgow, C2C: Country to Country will bring country music headliners together in one place, for one weekend!

faqs.question: When is Country to Country 2023 in Glasgow?
faqs.answer: Country to Country takes place in Glasgow on Friday 10th March, Saturday 11th March, and Sunday 12th March 2023.

faqs.question: Where is Country to Country in Glasgow?
faqs.answer: Country to Country Glasgow will take place at the OVO Hydro, Exhibition Way, Stobcross Rd, Glasgow G3 8YW.

faqs.question: Does Country to Country have any age restrictions?
faqs.answer:
No, this event is for all ages. (all ages require a ticket)

 

Under 15's must be accompanied by adult.
